       <h3 class="text-center"><b>Your Hotels Will Appear Here</b></h1>
       <button type="button" id="newHotel" class="btn btn-primary" data-toggle="modal" data-target="#addHotel">Click Here To Add Hotel</button>
       <div class="entry">
